### Register User
POST http://localhost:6600/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "test2",
    "email": "test2@gmail.com",
    "password": "123"
}



### Login User
POST http://localhost:6600/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test2@gmail.com",
    "password": "123"
}



